<li id="cite_note-38"><b><a href="#cite_ref-38" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFNathan_Myhrvold">Nathan Myhrvold. <a href="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB114368437650611883.html" class="external text" title="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB114368437650611883.html" rel="nofollow">"<i>Inventors Have Rights, Too!</i>"</a>. Wall Street Journal<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB114368437650611883.html" class="external free" title="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB114368437650611883.html" rel="nofollow">http://online.wsj.com/article/SB114368437650611883.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%27%27Inventors+Have+Rights%2C+Too%21%27%27&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Nathan+Myhrvold&amp;rft.au=Nathan+Myhrvold&amp;rft.pub=Wall+Street+Journal&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB114368437650611883.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Patent_troll"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-39"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFStefanie_Olsen2004">Stefanie Olsen (August 9 2004). <a href="http://news.com.com/Google,+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet/2100-1024_3-5302421.html" class="external text" title="http://news.com.com/Google,+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet/2100-1024_3-5302421.html" rel="nofollow">"Google, Yahoo bury the legal hatchet"</a>. CNET<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://news.com.com/Google,+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet/2100-1024_3-5302421.html" class="external free" title="http://news.com.com/Google,+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet/2100-1024_3-5302421.html" rel="nofollow">http://news.com.com/Google,+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet/2100-1024_3-5302421.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Google%2C+Yahoo+bury+the+legal+hatchet&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Stefanie+Olsen&amp;rft.au=Stefanie+Olsen&amp;rft.date=August+9+2004&amp;rft.pub=CNET&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.com.com%2FGoogle%2C%2BYahoo%2Bbury%2Bthe%2Blegal%2Bhatchet%2F2100-1024_3-5302421.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Patent_troll"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
